rows.label: qst104215_msg0003
rows.name:
Fancy seeing you here.
Did you want something?

rows.label: qst104215_msg0006
rows.name: It's quite an interesting place, Liberalitas.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0007
rows.name:
Paths in between the islands
look quite like roots.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0008
rows.name:
All right. I'll teach the kids.
Once I finish my work.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0009
rows.name:
Bring me a rare root.
From Spirit Crucible Elpys.
Then I'll help.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0061
rows.name:
Find me a Colla Carrot.
From a remote area of Elpys.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0062
rows.name:
Villagers told me not to go alone.
Said there were monsters.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0063
rows.name:
You lot'll be fine though.
Good luck.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0121
rows.name:
Look for a beautiful lake.
That's where it is.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0122
rows.name:
Make sure you get it right.
It's a Colla Carrot. A root.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0151
rows.name:
A Colla Carrot!
Good job. I'll teach the kids.

rows.label: qst104215_msg0152
rows.name:
Let me go back to my lab.
Gotta make preparations.
Then I'll head to the village.
